00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:02,001 --> 00:00:06,756
(Episode 2: Soul Check-In)

2
00:00:07,006 --> 00:00:08,508
Haa... Handle it quickly.

3
00:00:11,302 --> 00:00:12,512
Take care of it quickly!

4
00:00:13,471 --> 00:00:15,765
Ah, I'm sorry, I...

5
00:00:16,099 --> 00:00:18,560
It's seeping in... That's enough, stop!

6
00:00:28,737 --> 00:00:29,821
Throw it away.

7
00:00:32,574 --> 00:00:33,491
Yes...

8
00:00:51,634 --> 00:00:52,969
I'm... sorry.

9
00:00:53,386 --> 00:00:55,180
I didn't realize you were the boss.

10
00:00:57,015 --> 00:00:57,974
It's fine.

11
00:00:57,974 --> 00:01:00,769
Well, as you know,
running a guesthouse means

12
00:01:00,769 --> 00:01:03,146
sometimes drinking together
with the guests...

13
00:01:03,146 --> 00:01:06,232
and chatting with them
is part of the job...

14
00:01:06,733 --> 00:01:09,027
Right, that makes sense.

15
00:01:09,569 --> 00:01:12,113
You're pretty cool about it, Boss.

16
00:01:12,405 --> 00:01:13,907
You're just going to let it slide?

17
00:01:14,407 --> 00:01:17,410
No, it's hopeless.

18
00:01:17,744 --> 00:01:18,495
Huh?

19
00:01:18,495 --> 00:01:21,915
Then...
you're not firing me, right?

20
00:01:22,123 --> 00:01:24,209
You've trusted me with this place all this time.

21
00:01:25,376 --> 00:01:27,629
Yeah, fine.

22
00:01:28,046 --> 00:01:29,255
Really?

23
00:01:29,255 --> 00:01:33,259
Ha... Thank you.
I'll work really hard.

24
00:01:36,387 --> 00:01:38,348
You can stay until it's sold.

25
00:01:38,681 --> 00:01:39,724
Excuse me?

26
00:01:40,809 --> 00:01:42,393
- Secretary Ha.
- Yes, President.

27
00:01:43,478 --> 00:01:45,313
Rip out all this tacky stuff.

28
00:01:45,688 --> 00:01:49,150
If we remodel it luxuriously
and rebrand it with a premium image,

29
00:01:49,150 --> 00:01:50,318
it might be presentable.

30
00:01:50,318 --> 00:01:52,445
You're selling Badam Stay?

31
00:01:52,904 --> 00:01:53,571
Yeah.

32
00:01:53,571 --> 00:01:56,533
Ah, but you promised the previous boss.

33
00:01:56,533 --> 00:01:58,326
That you'd keep this place as it is.

34
00:01:58,326 --> 00:02:00,537
Words are cheap in business.

35
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,873
- You absolutely can't do that here.
- Is there nowhere else for you to make money?

36
00:02:04,165 --> 00:02:06,417
There should be plenty of places that pay more than here.

37
00:02:06,626 --> 00:02:08,962
I didn't work here for the money.

38
00:02:08,962 --> 00:02:09,921
Then what?

39
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,382
Because it's a precious place.

40
00:02:12,966 --> 00:02:14,634
Because it has value.

41
00:02:15,468 --> 00:02:16,970
I imagined the boss

42
00:02:17,345 --> 00:02:19,597
was someone

43
00:02:20,306 --> 00:02:21,850
who recognized that value.

44
00:02:21,850 --> 00:02:23,685
Does value that doesn't make money

45
00:02:24,894 --> 00:02:25,979
even count as value?

46
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:27,939
What?

47
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:32,443
You live like that
because you cling to such pathetic sentiments.

48
00:02:37,031 --> 00:02:40,451
I'll be staying here for a while.
Show me to the best room.

49
00:02:52,171 --> 00:02:56,342
Does value that doesn't make money... even count as value?

50
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:17,280
- Yoon Jio, is this all you can do?
- Why are you so irresponsible?

51
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,657
- It's a complete mess.
- I told you to redo it.

52
00:04:06,162 --> 00:04:07,413
Thank you.

53
00:04:47,704 --> 00:04:49,497
Because it has value.

54
00:04:50,290 --> 00:04:56,212
I imagined the boss was someone
who recognized that value.

55
00:05:17,233 --> 00:05:18,192
Huh?

56
00:05:23,823 --> 00:05:24,824
Whoa!

57
00:06:07,241 --> 00:06:08,367
- Oh!
- Ah!

58
00:06:16,501 --> 00:06:18,336
H-hey, where are you looking?!

59
00:06:18,753 --> 00:06:22,215
You're the one... exposing yourself.

60
00:06:29,472 --> 00:06:30,598
What's that sound?

61
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:40,316
Huh...?

62
00:06:42,944 --> 00:06:44,153
Wait a minute!

63
00:09:17,181 --> 00:09:19,892
Why did I get... so big?

64
00:09:30,319 --> 00:09:31,904
Aaaagh!

65
00:09:32,738 --> 00:09:34,532
Aaaagh!

66
00:09:37,827 --> 00:09:39,912
Why is it so loud?

67
00:09:59,348 --> 00:10:00,558
My muscles.

68
00:10:03,477 --> 00:10:05,104
Where did my muscles go?

69
00:10:33,674 --> 00:10:38,054
- Aaaagh!
- Aaaagh!

70
00:10:54,278 --> 00:11:00,785
"Check In to You"

